{"tid":1800060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除夕想同手足們一齊倒數，踏入新一年繼續抗爭！","createTime":"2019-12-27T12:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T23:51:31.000Z","uid":62369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f43bb38bf3f0dcbdbe2d70cd0a5608ec21be19d","tid":1800060,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1，2，光，復，香，港，時，代，革，命！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我係踏入2020年嘅一刻想同眾義士一齊過，<br />\n話比大家知新一年會繼續抗爭。<br />\n當誓師大會又好，當第二日元旦遊行前嘅集氣大會又好。<br />\n<br />\n我知31號7:00有除夕人鏈，又可能有和你shop 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果9:00-9:30 係各大倒數熱點開始集合好唔好？<br />\n銅鑼灣Time square /sogo?<br />\n中環蘭桂坊<br />\n尖沙咀海港城或海旁？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n除咗願榮光之外一齊唱不屈進行曲歌詞好適合<br />\n<br />\n來同行 看見嗎<br />\n大地上 不屈的心<br />\n告眾義士 即使險惡<br />\n也奮力 來驅走 昏暗<br />\n在黎明前 你聽見嗎<br />\n是濁霧下 鏗鏘吼聲<br />\n告眾弟妹 不屈的你<br />\n會照亮明天的 香港<br />\n為大義 來一起奮抗戰<br />\n讓熱淚 和鮮血 沒白掉<br />\n銘記 眾同伴獻身 約誓<br />\n願萬代 仍堅守這要塞<br />\n讓願望 能歸依這家邦<br />\n在 絕地 屹立 共建光輝<br />\n將正義 歸萬眾"},{"pid":"0a77fc7187ee67cd3c932c77bf949208b2ae5678","tid":1800060,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3d08cb405887cd4bd4e0fc233cd04b3c6587db","tid":1800060,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db43cb792e37ec492b22b0fd83e665fdaa3e4f5","tid":1800060,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78d5ff7f9e35f9347bec49db75f7fea6c6952fe","tid":1800060,"uid":101034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}